ir duty cycle. This pattern has a high\nsignal-to-noise ratio for the brightest quasar in a typical SKA shallow survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Feb 2018 09:45:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-06"}
